CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

July 29, 2014

[Cite as 0712912014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-3296.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2014-0846. State ex rel. Sultaana v. Bova.

Cuyahoga App. No. 100875, 2014-Ohio-1737. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County.

Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal, it is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.

It is further ordered that a mandate be sent to and filed with the clerk of the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County:
